511
00:35:43,477 --> 00:35:45,687
Gosto mesmo deste casaco.

512
00:35:46,355 --> 00:35:48,482
Vou levar a minha miúda a jantar com ele.

513
00:35:48,565 --> 00:35:51,318
- Sim?
- Imagina as insígnias e as medalhas.

514
00:35:51,401 --> 00:35:52,986
